thread.title: KWSP on 3D Printing in motorsport

title: KWSP on 3D Printing in motorsport
text:
Expand KWSP on 3D printing parts for Le Mans 24 The second video in our TCT Show + Personalize 2015 Conference Series comes from Kieron Salter, Managing Director at KW Special Projects , who takes to the NEC stage to talk about a digital manufacturing project with Strakka Racing to design and manufacture a complete driver safety and door protection system for a Le Mans race car. 
To keep up-to-date on all the latest videos from TCT Show make sure you subscribe to our YouTube channel. Tags
